Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（フィル）エヘヘッ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,うっ…
